@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<div>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>
        At [Your Website Name], we are committed to protecting the privacy and
        security of our website visitors and users. This privacy policy explains
        the types of personal data we collect, how we use it, and who we may
        share it with.
    </p>
    <br />
    <br /> <h3>What personal data we collect</h3> <br />
    <ul>
        <li>
            We collect personal data that you provide to us directly, such as your
            name, email address, and phone number when you fill out a contact form
            or sign up for our newsletter.
        </li>
        <li>
            We may collect personal data automatically through cookies or similar
            technologies when you visit our website. This data may include your IP
            address, browser type, device type, and other usage information.
        </li>
        <li>
            We may collect personal data from third-party sources, such as social
            media platforms, if you interact with our website through those
            platforms.
        </li>
    </ul>
    <br />
    <br />
    <h3>How we use your personal data</h3>
    <br />
    <ul>
        <li>
            We use your personal data to provide and improve our services, such as
            responding to your inquiries, processing your orders, and sending you
            newsletters or promotional emails.
        </li>
        <li>
            We may use your personal data for marketing purposes, such as to
            personalize our advertising and to measure the effectiveness of our
            marketing campaigns.
        </li>
        <li>
            We may use your personal data to comply with legal or regulatory
            requirements.
        </li>
    </ul>
    <br />
    <br />
    <h3>Who we may share your personal data with</h3>
    <br />
    <ul>
        <li>
            We may share your personal data with third-party service providers who
            assist us with our business operations, such as hosting, analytics,
            and marketing.
        </li>
        <li>
            We may share your personal data with third-party partners for
            marketing purposes, such as to show you personalized advertisements.
        </li>
        <li>
            We may share your personal data if required by law or to protect our
            legal rights.
        </li>
    </ul>
    <br />
    <br />
    <h3>How we protect your personal data</h3>
    <br />
    <ul>
        <li>
            We take reasonable measures to protect your personal data from
            unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction.
        </li>
        <li>
            We restrict access to your personal data to employees and contractors
            who need to know that information in order to operate, develop, or
            improve our services.
        </li>
    </ul>
    <br />
    <br />
    <h3>Your rights regarding your personal data</h3>
    <br />
    <ul>
        <li>
            You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data
            that we hold.
        </li>
        <li>
            You have the right to object to or restrict the processing of your
            personal data.
        </li>
        <li>
            You have the right to withdraw your consent for us to use your
            personal data.
        </li>
    </ul>
    <br />
    <br /> <h3>Updates to this privacy policy</h3>
    <br />
    <ul>
        <li>
            We may update this privacy policy from time to time to reflect changes
            in our practices or legal requirements.
        </li>
        <li>
            We will notify you of any material changes to this privacy policy by
            posting the updated policy on our website.
        </li>
    </ul>
    <br />
    <br /> <h3>Contact us</h3>
    <br />
    <ul>
        <li>
            If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy policy or how
            we handle your personal data, please contact us at [Your Contact
            Email].
        </li>
    </ul>
</div>